    "encrypted": "false",
    "long_instructions": "## Can Your Trust the Bot?\r\n\r\n1. Start by asking a factual question in AI Chat.\r\n\r\n2. Check the Prompt\r\n\t- Ask: \"Can you cite a source?\"\r\n\t- Add a trusted source: \"According to[source]...\"\r\n\t- Be more specific in your prompt\r\n\r\n3. Check the Facts\r\n\t- Search trusted websites\r\n\t- Compare answers from multiple sources\r\n\t- Look for named experts or dates in the response\r\n\r\n<br/>\r\n\r\n<details>\r\n  <summary><strong>Not sure what question to test? See some examples below.</strong></summary>\r\n  <ul>\r\n\r\n    <li>What's the most recent Nobel Prize in Literature?</li>\r\n    <li>How many Supreme Court justices are there right now?</li>\r\n    <li>Who won Best Hip-Hop Album at the most recent Grammys?</li>\r\n    <li>When was the first computer invented?</li>\r\n    <li>Who won the last World Cup?</li>\r\n  </ul>\r\n</details>\r\n\r\n",
